'''Letekidan Micael''' (wavutse 1997), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri  [[Eritereya]] .  ''Azwiho'' uruhare rwa 'Awet' muri filime Feuerherz ishimwa cyane.   

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1997 i [[Asmara]], muri [[Eritereya]].  Igihe ''yakinaga muri firime yintambara ya Feuerherz'', umuryango we wakiriye ubutumwa bwiterabwoba butazwi. Ni yo mpamvu bashatse ubuhungiro bwa politiki mu [[Burayi]]. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2008, Micael afite imyaka 10, yakinnye muri filime yo mu [[Budage]] ''Feuerherz'', nyuma yitwa Icyongereza nka  ''Heart of Fire'' .   Yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 25 Nzeri 2008. Iyi filime yerekanwe mu ntambara yo kwigenga ya [[Eritereya]] na [[Etiyopiya]], ikaba yari ishingiye ku mibereho y’umuhanzi w’umudage Senait Mehari wavukiye muri [[Eritereya]]. Iyi filime yakiriwe neza n'abayinenga kandi ishima uruhare rwa Micael nk'umusirikare w'umwana, 'Awet'.  

